## Limitations

The report is based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. The findings are limited to the insights provided by the selected sources, and there may be additional factors influencing the impact of coaches on players that were not covered. Furthermore, the search did not include empirical studies or interviews with athletes, which could provide more in-depth understanding.